data.name: lb_help_crashes
data.value: 1. If it disconnects you, please try to switch off the tweaks one by one to see which caused it. 2. Attempt to disable map tweaks. 3. Examine the DLCs and STD patches for updates. 4. Check the game language. If you are on a Korean or Chinese client, please download the [STD] Language patch.

data.name: lb_help_jukebox
data.value: The Custom Jukebox is one of the tweaks. It changes the in-game traditional jukebox (game music) into your fully customisable one. To use it, install DLC3. Select the song you like and then add it. Then you are all set!

data.name: lb_help_map
data.value: Map (or so-called court) tweaks is one of the tweaks. It changes the in-game traditional maps into the ones that the program offers. To use it, download the DLC next to each option and select the map you want. In the configuration page, you can also change its variant.

data.name: lb_help_patches
data.value: The patches will apply the patches fetched from the server to the game. They will be overwritten by official game patches every time you launch the game. Except [STD], aka Standalones. To use, just click on "Patch it" and wait for the game to start. You can also apply multiple patches by holding down the control key and selecting the patches you want.

data.name: lb_help_tips
data.value: 1. Perform all tweaks before applying patches. 2. You can hide the program by double clicking on the cat icon in the task bar. 3. If there's a bug, please report it to me. 4. It's bad to commit suicide.

data.name: lb_help_tweaks
data.value: Unlike patches, tweaks don't need to be redownloaded every time you launch the game. Tweaks will automatically apply any downloaded DLCs into the game in a legit way to avoid overwriting by official game patches. To begin, download the necessary DLCs and enable the desired tweaks.

data.name: lb_help_voice_changer
data.value: The voice changer is one of the tweaks; it changes the in-game traditional MC language into your desired one. To use it, download DLC6 and choose your language. Note that the in-game language will be overwritten by the setting you made in "Game Language". Because of that, you can also use it as a game translator (you will need the [STD] Language pack).

data.value:
Before you continue, please read this.
takattoFS2 Patcher is not a hack tool. I do not encourage people to use hacks or cheats, and this program has nothing to do with it.
takattoFS2 Patcher violates Joycity's terms of service by modifying the client, although there is no evidence that Joycity takes actions against users who use it. Your account is not at risk for simply using takattoFS2 Patcher alone. Abusing the service or using patches which further violate the Terms of Service can get your account terminated, however. All patches and tweaks from my official repository are safe.
takattoFS2 Patcher is not something Joycity don't know about. In fact, they acknowledged its existence and allowed me to work on some parts of the game.
takattoFS2 Patcher does not collect your personal data and this program has no ability to do so. There is no connection outside the main server, which is Github, so you can rest assured!
That's it! Happy gaming (^w^) - a cat lover~
